# getGJUserList20.php

Gets either your friend list or your blocked list

## Parameters

### Required Parameters

**accountID** - The account ID of the user you want to get the friends/blocklist of

**gjp** - The [GJP](/topics/encryption/gjp.md) of the user you want to get the friends/blocklist of

**secret** - Wmfd2893gb7

### Optional Parameters

**gameVersion** - 21

**binaryVersion** - 35

**gdw** - 0

**type** - 0 for friends, 1 for blocklist. Defaults to 0 if left out

## Response

A list of [user objects](/resources/server/user.md) based on which list you choose, separated by pipes `|`.

## Example

<!-- tabs:start -->

### **Python**

```py
import requests

data = {
        "accountID": 173831, # DevExit's account ID
        "gjp": "********", # This would be DevExit's password encoded with GJP encryption
        "secret": "Wmfd2893gb7"
}

req = requests.post("http://boomlings.com/database/getGJUserList20.php", data=data)
print(req.text)
```
